data.description: Stunning Aliante Pool Home * 4 bedroom and 3 Full Baths plus 2 Family Rooms * Located in Aliante* Excellent walking location next to Nature Discovery Park & Aliante Shopping Complex. Easy commute to Nellis or Creech AFB. Tons of space inside & out. Solar electric power for low utilities. Fully finished backyard includes pool, wet deck entry, 3 water spout/features, with solar heating, Astroturf, and Alumawood covered patio to enjoy all summer long. Open flooplan layout and kitchen w/stainless steel appliances, granite counters, tile in the main walking areas plus plush carpet in the bedrooms. Spacious laundry room upstairs. Generous space downstairs for guests w/ bedroom & full bath. Large secondary bedrooms upstairs. Spacious primary suite upstairs and walk-in closet. Huge den/second family room or convert to an oversized 5th bedroom if needed. Water treatment system and reverse osmosis. Pride of Ownership! Check out the Virtual Tour Link to the Matterport walking tour as well.
